flowchart TD
    Start([START]) --> WP

    subgraph Orchestrator[Top-level orchestrator graph\ngraph/builder.py]
        direction TD
        WP[work_planner\n(subgraph node)]
        RouteWP{"_route_after_work_planner\nstate.error?"}
        AA[await_approval\ninterrupt()]
        RouteAA{"_route_after_approval\napproval_decision"}
        EX[execute_plan]
        End([END])

        WP --> RouteWP
        RouteWP -->|error set| End
        RouteWP -->|no error| AA
        AA --> RouteAA
        RouteAA -->|approved| EX
        RouteAA -->|rejected/other| End
        EX --> End
    end

    subgraph WorkPlanner[work_planner subgraph internals\ngraph/work_planner/builder.py]
        direction TD
        VI[validate_input]
        CD[check_duplicate]
        FT[fetch_ticket]
        CWR[create_workflow_record]
        GP[generate_plan]
        VP[validate_plan]
        AWC[await_workplan_clarification\ninterrupt()]
        SP[store_plan]
        PTJ[post_to_jira]
        EH[error_handler]
        WPEnd([END])

        VI --> RVI{"route_after_validate_input"}
        RVI -->|ok| CD
        RVI -->|error| EH

        CD --> RCD{"route_after_check_duplicate"}
        RCD -->|ok| FT
        RCD -->|error| EH

        FT --> RFT{"route_after_fetch_ticket"}
        RFT -->|ok| CWR
        RFT -->|error| EH

        CWR --> GP

        GP --> RGP{"route_after_generate_plan"}
        RGP -->|work_plan_data + no error| VP
        RGP -->|error or missing plan| EH

        VP --> RVP{"route_after_validate_plan"}
        RVP -->|status pass + no questions| SP
        RVP -->|status concerns/blocked\nor questions_for_reviewer| AWC
        RVP -->|error| EH

        AWC --> RAWC{"route_after_workplan_clarification"}
        RAWC -->|clarification received| GP
        RAWC -->|error| EH

        SP --> PTJ --> WPEnd
        EH --> WPEnd
    end

    WP -. expands to .-> VI
